{"id":221164,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/04/global-voices-巴基斯坦：喀拉蚩暴力事件层出不穷/","date":"2012-04-18T09:17:29Z","modified":"2012-04-18T09:17:29Z","title":"Global Voices | 巴基斯坦：喀拉蚩暴力事件层出不穷","content":"<p><p>最近三个月来造成喀拉蚩<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://dunyanews.tv/index.php?key=Q2F0SUQ9MiNOaWQ9NzM4MzA=\" href=\"http://dunyanews.tv/index.php?key=Q2F0SUQ9MiNOaWQ9NzM4MzA=\">超过三百人</a>死亡的流血事件仍在继续。最新一起发生在属于喀拉蚩最大政党统一民族运动党（<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Muttahida_Qaumi_Movement\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Muttahida_Qaumi_Movement\">MQM</a>）的政治运动者 Mansoor Mukhtar <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://dawn.com/2012/03/27/mqm-announces-day-of-mourning-in-sindh-today/\" href=\"http://dawn.com/2012/03/27/mqm-announces-day-of-mourning-in-sindh-today/\">被杀</a>隔天的三月廿八日，<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Awami_National_Party\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Awami_National_Party\">ANP</a>（人民民族党）的 Zianulabdeen 遭不明恐怖份子谋杀。</p>\n<p>这些以敲诈勒索和有目标的凶杀堆叠而成的谋杀案引起残暴的连锁反应，使这个港口城蒙上一层阴影。新闻网站 <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://dawn.com/2012/03/27/industry-of-manufactured-violence-2012/\" href=\"http://dawn.com/2012/03/27/industry-of-manufactured-violence-2012/\">Dawn 的时间表</a>整理了到四月九日为止的事件。</p>\n<p>最关键的问题是，“为什么喀拉蚩总是脱离不了暴力？”</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.demotix.com/photo/1133848/least-13-killed-24-hours-during-political-violence-karachi\"><img title=\"Rangers stand guard next to a burnt out car that was set on fire after a shooting incident, which killed Awami National Party (ANP) activist in Karachi. Image by Mohsin Hasan. Copyright Demotix.\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/1133848-640x480.jpg\" alt=\"Rangers stand guard next to a burnt out car that was set on fire after a shooting incident, which killed Awami National Party (ANP) activist in Karachi. Image by Mohsin Hasan. Copyright Demotix.\" width=\"350\" height=\"233\" /></a></p>\n<p>骑警在烧毁的车辆旁戒备。这部车在造成一名人民民族党（ANP）活跃人士死亡的枪击后遭纵火焚烧。照片来自 Mohsin Hasan，版权为 Demotix 所有。</p>\n</div>\n<p>去年共有<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://tribune.com.pk/story/269861/political-parties-harbour-private-militias-criminal-gangs/\" href=\"http://tribune.com.pk/story/269861/political-parties-harbour-private-militias-criminal-gangs/\">一千一百七十五人</a>遭到杀害，造成这些暴力事件的原因众多，例如：</p>\n<p>1. 人们<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://dawn.com/2011/08/28/ethnic-fault-lines-of-karachi/\" href=\"http://dawn.com/2011/08/28/ethnic-fault-lines-of-karachi/\">因为错误的理由对立</a>，像是种族、文化、语言和宗教派系。甚至在不同社区内部也存在对立，这些冲突催化了城市的“战争语言”。不同的利益团体有不同的目标，权力自然是其中之一。一丁点火花就足以引爆大量的暴力事件。最近四个月内喀拉蚩举办了国内最多的政治集会，像是 <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://dawn.com/2011/12/25/more-than-200000-expected-to-attend-pti-rally/\" href=\"http://dawn.com/2011/12/25/more-than-200000-expected-to-attend-pti-rally/\">Tahreek-e-Insaaf</a>（正义运动）、<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://tribune.com.pk/story/338707/mqms-holds-worlds-largest-women-rally-in-karachi/\" href=\"http://tribune.com.pk/story/338707/mqms-holds-worlds-largest-women-rally-in-karachi/\">MQM（联合民族运动）妇女</a>、右翼的 <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://tribune.com.pk/story/335233/public-rally-difa-e-pakistan-bandwagon-rolls-into-karachi/\" href=\"http://tribune.com.pk/story/335233/public-rally-difa-e-pakistan-bandwagon-rolls-into-karachi/\">Defa-e-Pakistan（保卫巴基斯坦）</a>和 <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://tribune.com.pk/story/327994/people-with-luxurious-lifestyles-cannot-bring-islamic-revolution/\" href=\"http://tribune.com.pk/story/327994/people-with-luxurious-lifestyles-cannot-bring-islamic-revolution/\">JUI（伊斯兰教士会）</a>、<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.dailytimes.com.pk/default.asp?page=2012%5C03%5C24%5Cstory_24-3-2012_pg7_28\" href=\"http://www.dailytimes.com.pk/default.asp?page=2012%5C03%5C24%5Cstory_24-3-2012_pg7_28\">JSQM（信德民族运动）</a>，以及右翼的 <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://geokarachi.blogspot.com/2012/02/diffa-e-tashiyo-conference.html\" href=\"http://geokarachi.blogspot.com/2012/02/diffa-e-tashiyo-conference.html\">Defa-e-Tashishu（保卫什叶派）</a>。这些集会各自集结了为数众多的支持者，这个城市在意识形态上的分裂可见一斑。</p>\n<p>2. 政党拥兵自重。根据 HRCP（巴基斯坦人权委员会）的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://tribune.com.pk/story/269861/political-parties-harbour-private-militias-criminal-gangs/\" href=\"http://tribune.com.pk/story/269861/political-parties-harbour-private-militias-criminal-gangs/\">报告</a>，喀拉蚩主要的政党都有私人民兵部队。这些部队被用来确保既得利益，造成社区分裂，引发暴力。去年最高法院主动下令解散这些部队，然而并没有任何实际行动。</p>\n<p>3. <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.radioopensource.org/mohammed-hanif-the-explosive-case-of-karachi/\" href=\"http://www.radioopensource.org/mohammed-hanif-the-explosive-case-of-karachi/\">人口过剩</a>、缺乏计划。本市人口从 1947 年的五十万成长到 1970 年代的五百万，现在则是惊人的两千万。另一方面却没有足够的基础建设发展因应这些大量流入的人口。这两样因素加起来导致居民的经济情况恶化，让犯罪团体有了加以利用并获取个人利益的机会。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://tribune.com.pk/story/361617/why-karachi-burns-again-and-again/\" href=\"http://tribune.com.pk/story/361617/why-karachi-burns-again-and-again/\">Pervez Hoodbhoy</a> 用鱼作比方解释人口过剩的影响。根据研究，鱼群有两个目标：他们希望在鱼缸里（一）取得更多可用空间，（二）增加栖息区域中可用的结构（像是石块或植物之类可供躲藏的障碍物）。当鱼的数量增加，可用空间相对减少，鱼群的攻击性就增加了。</p>\n<p>Hoodbhoy 认为喀拉蚩的情况也是如此，基础设施多年来消耗殆尽。他引用 <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eqbal_Ahmad\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eqbal_Ahmad\">Eqbal Ahmed</a> 的文章说：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>喀拉蚩无法享用自己创造出的财富。它贡献了全国和信德省政府超过百分之六十的税收，但只有一小部份回流用以建设这个城市。更糟的是，历任市政府当权者都贪婪的搜刮它的土地和资源。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.demotix.com/photo/1081669/five-dead-bodies-found-karachi\"><img title=\"People gather at the house where the dead bodies of five people were found. Image by PPI Images. Copyright Demotix.\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/1081669-640x480.jpg\" alt=\"People gather at the house where the dead bodies of five people were found. Image by PPI Images. Copyright Demotix.\" width=\"500\" height=\"349\" /></a></p>\n<p>人民在发现五名死者的房屋前集结。图片来自 PPI Images。版权为 Demotix 所有。</p>\n</div>\n<p>一般市民对本市目前的情况感到极度沮丧。青少年看不出近期有任何正面发展的可能，言谈中充满了绝望的阴影，唯一能做的只有请求上帝赐给他们一个美好的未来。青少年对于喀拉蚩的乱象的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://blogs.tribune.com.pk/story/7687/karachi-violence-what-teenagers-think/\" href=\"http://blogs.tribune.com.pk/story/7687/karachi-violence-what-teenagers-think/\">评论</a>如下：</p>\n<p>Natasha Faisal 说：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>我环顾周遭并纳闷，分裂的我们无法为国家带来发展，怎么可能兴盛。我不明白我们为何变得如此冷酷，不再为同胞的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://tribune.com.pk/story/203309/hrcp-report-indicates-rise-in-killings-this-year/\" href=\"http://tribune.com.pk/story/203309/hrcp-report-indicates-rise-in-killings-this-year/\">死亡</a>哀伤？</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Mirha Khan 说：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>看着最近在喀拉蚩的暴力事件数量，我常常想这个城市是不是有一天会被烧成灰烬？</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Malika Niazi 说：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>现在我们能做的只有为喀拉蚩的未来祈祷。人们接连死去，不带武器在街上乱逛实在很不安全。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>推特和脸书上涌入失望和批评的留言，要求政府阻止这些暴力事件。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/royjawad/posts/10150633733871946\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/royjawad/posts/10150633733871946\">Jawad Hussain</a>：喀拉蚩市再度陷入暴力漩涡。今天早上我在古利斯坦区看到几个坏蛋放火烧掉一辆迷你巴士，同时还有消息指出，在包括巴尔迪亚镇之内的几个都会区有无辜的人被害。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/parasabbasi/status/188339275203485697\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/parasabbasi/status/188339275203485697\">@parasabbasi</a>：今天做了个怪梦，梦见我和两个朋友出去买药，却变成枪击的目标。（<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/search/%23Karachi\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/search/%23Karachi\">#喀拉蚩</a>暴力）</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Nadeem Paracha 质疑谁是喀拉蚩真正的恐怖份子？</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/NadeemfParacha/status/89586057531756544\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/NadeemfParacha/status/89586057531756544\">@NadeemfParacha</a>：今天的报纸上那么多关于喀拉蚩暴力事件的报导，却完全没提是谁在杀害谁？</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Jaffrry 在推特上表示政府必须采取行动：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/Jaffrry/status/188253977673080832\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/Jaffrry/status/188253977673080832\">@Jaffrry</a>：政府必须采取适当措施阻止这些暴力。<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/search/%23Karachi\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/search/%23Karachi\">#喀拉蚩</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Soup\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80E5%B7%B4%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%EF%BC%9A%E5%96%80%E6%8B%89%E8%9A%A9%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E5%B1%82%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%8D%E7%A9%B7&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F18%2F10814%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F18%2F10814%2F&#038;desc=%E5%B7%B4%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%EF%BC%9A%E5%96%80%E6%8B%89%E8%9A%A9%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E5%B1%82%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%8D%E7%A9%B7\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F18%2F10814%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F18%2F10814%2F&#038;text=%E5%B7%B4%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%EF%BC%9A%E5%96%80%E6%8B%89%E8%9A%A9%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E5%B1%82%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%8D%E7%A9%B7&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F18%2F10814%2F&#038;title=%E5%B7%B4%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%EF%BC%9A%E5%96%80%E6%8B%89%E8%9A%A9%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E5%B1%82%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%8D%E7%A9%B7\" title=\"reddit\"><span>reddit</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.stumbleupon.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F18%2F10814%2F&#038;title=%E5%B7%B4%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%EF%BC%9A%E5%96%80%E6%8B%89%E8%9A%A9%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E5%B1%82%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%8D%E7%A9%B7\" title=\"StumbleUpon\"><span>StumbleUpon</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://del.icio.us/post?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F18%2F10814%2F&#038;title=%E5%B7%B4%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%EF%BC%9A%E5%96%80%E6%8B%89%E8%9A%A9%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E5%B1%82%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%8D%E7%A9%B7\" title=\"delicious\"><span>delicious</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.instapaper.com/edit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F18%2F10814%2F&#038;title=%E5%B7%B4%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%EF%BC%9A%E5%96%80%E6%8B%89%E8%9A%A9%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E5%B1%82%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%8D%E7%A9%B7\" title=\"Instapaper\"><span>Instapaper</span></a></span></p>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=735659\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"735659\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/embeddedform?formkey=dGRpN3FrVThuMFFsZHBZcmNGLW94dEE6MQ\" width=\"450\" height=\"309\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\">Loading&#8230;</iframe></p>\n","author":1004,"categories":[20534],"tags":[]}